{"title":"斥美国战争狂人","authors":["郭沫若"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":9,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"斥美国战争狂人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郭沫若"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战争狂人可恶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横行霸道无谱！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才在西亚弄兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又想对我动武。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁不知道台湾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它是中国领土？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个历史事实，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比你美国还古。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可恨一撮败类，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卖国卖身为虏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甘做美国傀儡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公然认贼作父。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因此台湾澎湖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连及金门马祖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尚被狂人霸占，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九年未归故土。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民忍耐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作为悬案待处；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等待适当时期，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放全部岛屿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁知美国狂人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更加喧宾夺主！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妄想发动战争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"继承轴心步武。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搬出炮舰政策，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是时代错误。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请问希莫东条，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今竟在何处？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侵朝战争何如？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侵黎罪行受阻！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂人总是健忘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"失掉全部脑髓！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日人民中国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不容狂人低估！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日中国人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不容受人欺侮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民精神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢想敢说敢做；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任何天大威胁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无畏无忧无睹！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们有力自卫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保护神圣领土。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六亿人民皆兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决不后退半步！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你有热核潜艇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只能哄走魟鱼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你有原子武器，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只能骇倒老鼠！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杜勒斯和艾克，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一万个何补！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么“战争边缘”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任你叫破狗肚！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是师出无名，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是得道多助。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战友遍满世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁怕纸糊老虎？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苏联东欧兄弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是和平干卤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亚非拉丁美洲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是反战伴侣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不闻十手所指，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫人无病鸣呼？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何况疯狂无边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干犯人类众怒？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫你狂人清醒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫再操刀自屠！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台湾海峡不宽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会是你的坟墓！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有眼不识泰山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢来头上动土；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫你有去无回，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义结束！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奉告欧美人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿出主人态度！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"制止战争狂人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫再放任踌蹰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了人类幸福，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"必须和平共处。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了防止瘟疫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"必须消灭病毒！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"制止战争狂人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是神圣任务。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们敢于担当，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿作人类前驱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要使人类平等，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永恒友爱互助。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要使世界风云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永由和平作主！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1958年9月7日"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}